2622
01:09:26,380 --> 01:09:27,360
 i jugozapadu

2623
01:09:27,360 --> 01:09:28,320
 Irana.

2624
01:09:28,320 --> 01:09:30,780
 40% oni samo bombardiraju

2625
01:09:30,780 --> 01:09:31,340
 ovo što gledamo.

2626
01:09:31,340 --> 01:09:32,760
 60% Irana

2627
01:09:32,760 --> 01:09:33,260
 nema ništa.

