01:09:34,840 --> 01:09:36,020
 Jer je to ogromna zemlja.

2631
01:09:36,020 --> 01:09:37,380
 Nemaju oni snaga

2632
01:09:37,380 --> 01:09:38,480
 da pokriju sve to.

