01:09:38,480 --> 01:09:38,940
 Nema.

2634
01:09:38,940 --> 01:09:39,740
 Razumijem.

2635
01:09:39,740 --> 01:09:41,540
 Samo to ljudi

2636
01:09:41,540 --> 01:09:42,540
 koji ne znaju ratove,

