2655
01:10:12,020 --> 01:10:14,020
 u svim elementima

2656
01:10:14,020 --> 01:10:15,700
 obavještajnog osigurnostog

2657
01:10:15,700 --> 01:10:16,780
 i vojnog sustava,

2658
01:10:16,780 --> 01:10:18,640
 svoje agente,

2659
01:10:18,640 --> 01:10:19,640
 svoje ove,

