01:10:27,280 --> 01:10:28,280
 da od toga nema ništa,

2667
01:10:28,280 --> 01:10:29,280
 onda su Rusi promijenili

2668
01:10:29,280 --> 01:10:30,120
 doktrinu,

2669
01:10:30,120 --> 01:10:31,660
 povlače snagi

2670
01:10:31,660 --> 01:10:32,220
 gdje mogu

2671
01:10:32,220 --> 01:10:33,060
 objektivno,

2672
01:10:33,060 --> 01:10:34,660
 struktuiraju snage

2673
01:10:34,660 --> 01:10:35,220
 i primijenjuju

2674
01:10:35,220 --> 01:10:36,220
