01:10:36,220 --> 01:10:37,680
 koja je pokazala rezultate,

2676
01:10:37,680 --> 01:10:39,000
 a to je doktrina Artičoke.

2677
01:10:39,000 --> 01:10:40,260
 To je za one

2678
01:10:40,260 --> 01:10:40,980
 koji ne znaju

2679
01:10:40,980 --> 01:10:41,840
