2685
01:10:48,040 --> 01:10:49,200
 onda nešto i naučiš,

2686
01:10:49,200 --> 01:10:50,500
 pa ima doktrina

2687
01:10:50,500 --> 01:10:52,060
 rakovog manevra,

2688
01:10:52,060 --> 01:10:52,460
 dakle,

2689
01:10:52,460 --> 01:10:53,920
 ta manevra unazad

2690
01:10:53,920 --> 01:10:54,880
 i tako,

2691
01:10:54,880 --> 01:10:55,960
 onda imaš doktrina

2692
01:10:55,960 --> 01:10:56,800
 obuhvata,

2693
01:10:56,800 --> 01:10:58,360
 moju dvozdrogog obuhvata

2694
01:10:58,360 --> 01:10:59,100
 i tako dalje.

2695
01:10:59,100 --> 01:11:00,040
 To je za njih

2696
01:11:00,040 --> 01:11:01,200
 koji nauče nepismeno,

2697
01:11:01,200 --> 01:11:02,220
 onda se nek se ne petlja

2698
01:11:02,220 --> 01:11:03,160
 u ono što ne znaju.

2699
01:11:04,880 --> 01:11:06,540
 i to je davalo rezultate.

2700
01:11:06,540 --> 01:11:07,760
 Da bi ti došao,

2701
01:11:07,760 --> 01:11:09,940
 e sad idemo na strategiju,

2702
01:11:09,940 --> 01:11:12,940
 vrhuna svojnog umijeća,

2703
01:11:12,940 --> 01:11:13,500
 to je, već idemo

2704
01:11:13,500 --> 01:11:14,820
 na vrhuna svojnog umijeća.

2705
01:11:14,820 --> 01:11:16,360
 Dakle, ti primjenjuješ

2706
01:11:16,360 --> 01:11:17,080
 tu doktrinu,

2707
01:11:17,080 --> 01:11:18,420
 znači, to je list po list

2708
01:11:18,420 --> 01:11:19,140
 od kidanje,

2709
01:11:19,140 --> 01:11:20,840
 da ti slomi,

2710
01:11:20,840 --> 01:11:22,060
 zato te operacije

2711
01:11:22,060 --> 01:11:22,680
 traju dugo,

2712
01:11:22,680 --> 01:11:23,380
 zato taj rat

2713
01:11:23,380 --> 01:11:24,000
 traje dugo,

2714
01:11:24,000 --> 01:11:25,460
 zato i ovaj traja u Ukrajini

2715
01:11:25,460 --> 01:11:26,320
 i traje još,

2716
01:11:26,320 --> 01:11:27,260
 vidite, peta godina.

2717
01:11:27,260 --> 01:11:30,760
 Da protivnik tvoj,

2718
01:11:30,760 --> 01:11:31,700
 a to pratiš,

2719
01:11:31,700 --> 01:11:32,180
 to se poče,

2720
01:11:32,180 --> 01:11:33,120
 to sve su zna,

2721
01:11:33,680 --> 01:11:36,380
 dosegne svoju vršnu projekciju,

2722
01:11:36,380 --> 01:11:39,120
 vršnu točku

2723
01:11:39,120 --> 01:11:40,200
 svoje projekcije moći.

2724
01:11:40,200 --> 01:11:40,900
 Dakle,

2725
01:11:40,900 --> 01:11:43,360
 onda ide pad

2726
01:11:43,360 --> 01:11:44,680
 njegove projekcije moći,

2727
01:11:44,680 --> 01:11:46,240
 on može biti brži,

2728
01:11:46,240 --> 01:11:46,800
 okomito,

2729
01:11:46,800 --> 01:11:48,360
 može biti polegnutiji,

2730
01:11:48,360 --> 01:11:49,120
 ali je pad.

2731
01:11:49,120 --> 01:11:49,880
 Dobro.

2732
01:11:49,880 --> 01:11:53,240
 Tada ti u tom trenutku pada,

2733
01:11:53,240 --> 01:11:56,560
 pokrećeš stratešku operaciju

2734
01:11:56,560 --> 01:11:58,580
 i završiš rat.

2735
01:11:58,580 --> 01:12:00,000
 Aha.

2736
01:12:00,000 --> 01:12:00,760
 To je pobjeda.

2737
01:12:00,760 --> 01:12:01,660
 E sada vidim.

2738
01:12:01,660 --> 01:12:03,360
 Znači, treba prepoznati trenutak.

2739
01:12:03,360 --> 01:12:03,780
 Tako je.

2740
01:12:03,780 --> 01:12:04,780
 To se inače zove

2741
01:12:04,780 --> 01:12:05,980
 točka preokreta.

2742
01:12:05,980 --> 01:12:08,780
 Znači, ti moraš kad ti padne onda.

2743
01:12:08,780 --> 01:12:11,280
 Evo, samo primjer naša da razumiju.

2744
01:12:11,280 --> 01:12:13,140
 Evo, svi znaju u domovinskom ratu.

2745
01:12:13,140 --> 01:12:15,620
 A ovdje se jedni stratek plenerte operacije.

2746
01:12:15,620 --> 01:12:18,040
 Vojno-oboještenu službu.

2747
01:12:18,040 --> 01:12:19,160
 Dakle, to je moja zadaća,

2748
01:12:19,160 --> 01:12:19,900
 moje službe.

2749
01:12:20,480 --> 01:12:21,280
 Ja sami samo na čelu.

2750
01:12:21,280 --> 01:12:23,680
 To su umni ljudi, pametni, analitičari.

2751
01:12:23,680 --> 01:12:25,360
 Doktor znanosti.

2752
01:12:25,360 --> 01:12:30,560
 Srpska projekcija vojne moćnosti.

2753
01:12:30,560 --> 01:12:31,280
 Dakle, tri države.

2754
01:12:31,280 --> 01:12:33,260
 Evo, vidiš, govorio njihovo tri.

2755
01:12:33,260 --> 01:12:33,660
 Zašto?

2756
01:12:33,660 --> 01:12:35,900
 Zato je u vrijeme zadnje,

2757
01:12:35,900 --> 01:12:38,100
