2758
01:12:38,100 --> 01:12:40,280
 Šta će ta Hrvatska vojska?

2759
01:12:41,280 --> 01:12:42,500
 Oni nikada nisu,

2760
01:12:42,500 --> 01:12:43,940
 i to je kod nas.

2761
01:12:43,940 --> 01:12:45,820
 Ono su nekak, ne znam,

2762
01:12:45,820 --> 01:12:46,660
 nečega ni mena,

2763
01:12:46,660 --> 01:12:48,860
 u nekom vodkastu isto je došao,

2764
01:12:48,860 --> 01:12:50,060
 pa tvrdio kako smo i babe,

2765
01:12:50,060 --> 01:12:51,940
 babe i dide protjerali,

2766
01:12:51,940 --> 01:12:52,880
 ostalo nikako bije.

2767
01:12:52,880 --> 01:12:54,340
 Pa nerazumnici jedni,

2768
01:12:54,340 --> 01:12:56,260
 pa više, više te štete nanosite

2769
01:12:56,260 --> 01:12:58,460
 nego Srbiju.

2770
01:12:58,460 --> 01:12:59,460
 Jer krivo govorite.

2771
01:12:59,460 --> 01:13:01,820
 Naime, mi smo ratovali

2772
01:13:01,820 --> 01:13:03,140
 proti tri srpske vojske.

2773
01:13:03,140 --> 01:13:04,180
 Ne jednu, nego tri.

2774
01:13:04,180 --> 01:13:05,320
 I sve tri smo pobjedili.

2775
01:13:05,320 --> 01:13:06,400
 Sve tri.

2776
01:13:06,400 --> 01:13:09,460
 Jena je bila srpska vojska.

2777
01:13:10,400 --> 01:13:11,220
 imala sve oružje,

2778
01:13:11,220 --> 01:13:12,420
 mi ništa nismo imali.

2779
01:13:12,420 --> 01:13:14,480
 A pa prijeli smo snagom žrtve.

2780
01:13:14,480 --> 01:13:16,380
 Stragun opredjedljenja,

2781
01:13:16,380 --> 01:13:18,540
 snagom umnog vojstva Tuđmana.

2782
01:13:18,540 --> 01:13:21,800
 Pa nisu Rusi slučajno dali

2783
01:13:21,800 --> 01:13:24,980
 odličje 1996. godine,

2784
01:13:24,980 --> 01:13:26,600
 1996. godine,

2785
01:13:26,600 --> 01:13:29,480
 Tuđmanu orden maršal Žukov.

2786
01:13:29,480 --> 01:13:30,700
 Ko je maršal Žukov?

2787
01:13:30,700 --> 01:13:32,380
 Najveći vojskovača

2788
01:13:32,380 --> 01:13:33,360
 drugog svjetskog rata,

2789
01:13:33,360 --> 01:13:35,280
 što mu svi do jedne države

2790
01:13:35,280 --> 01:13:36,360
 na zapadu priznaju

2791
01:13:36,360 --> 01:13:37,520
 da je najveći vojskovačak.

2792
01:13:37,520 --> 01:13:40,260
 A što je maršal Žukov?

2793
01:13:40,260 --> 01:13:41,260
 učinio.

2794
01:13:41,260 --> 01:13:43,320
 On je završio rat,

2795
01:13:43,320 --> 01:13:44,680
 treba završiti rat.

2796
01:13:44,680 --> 01:13:46,800
 Svaka budala može početi rat,

2797
01:13:46,800 --> 01:13:48,420
 a samo veliki stratezi

2798
01:13:48,420 --> 01:13:49,400
 znaju završiti rat.

2799
01:13:49,400 --> 01:13:51,640
 Zato ona ima,

2800
01:13:51,640 --> 01:13:53,420
 ali on nema iznaslu strategiju,

2801
01:13:53,420 --> 01:13:54,220
 govorim pojmove

2802
01:13:54,220 --> 01:13:54,920
 koje se javljaju u mediji.

2803
01:13:54,920 --> 01:13:55,340
 Razumijem.

2804
01:13:55,540 --> 01:13:58,700
 najveće umijeće vrhunac je

2805
01:13:58,700 --> 01:14:00,260
 završiti rat

2806
01:14:00,260 --> 01:14:02,400
 na način

2807
01:14:02,400 --> 01:14:04,340
 da za 20-30 godina

2808
01:14:04,340 --> 01:14:05,360
 ponovo ne vodiš rat.

2809
01:14:05,360 --> 01:14:07,380
 To je umijeće rata.

2810
01:14:07,380 --> 01:14:08,320
 Ej, sada Žukov,

2811
01:14:08,320 --> 01:14:09,040
 što je napravio?

2812
01:14:10,100 --> 01:14:11,940
 ušao u Berlin i digao zastav,

2813
01:14:11,940 --> 01:14:12,420
 ili tako?

2814
01:14:12,420 --> 01:14:14,380
 Što je napravio Tudžman?

2815
01:14:14,380 --> 01:14:16,840
 Ušao u Klinu.

2816
01:14:16,840 --> 01:14:17,840
 Digao zastavu.

2817
01:14:17,840 --> 01:14:19,040
 Vidite, zastavu digao.

2818
01:14:19,820 --> 01:14:20,980
 Dakle, Tudžman

2819
01:14:20,980 --> 01:14:22,520
 i zato su oni njemu dali.

2820
01:14:22,520 --> 01:14:23,920
 Odliče Rusi.

2821
01:14:23,920 --> 01:14:24,820
 Pa ti si,

2822
01:14:24,820 --> 01:14:26,840
 presedniče Tudžman,

2823
01:14:26,840 --> 01:14:28,360
 koji sam bio general,

2824
01:14:28,360 --> 01:14:30,580
 kaže, ti si vrijedan

2825
01:14:30,580 --> 01:14:32,460
 jednog Žukova.

2826
01:14:32,460 --> 01:14:33,720
 E, moji Hrvati,

2827
01:14:33,720 --> 01:14:34,920
 to van je domovinski rat.

2828
01:14:34,920 --> 01:14:37,340
 Jer je znao završiti rat,

2829
01:14:37,340 --> 01:14:39,020
 ali ne bi mogao završiti rat

2830
01:14:39,020 --> 01:14:40,760
 bez oluje.

2831
01:14:40,760 --> 01:14:43,140
 Pobjeda mora biti jasna

2832
01:14:43,140 --> 01:14:43,780
 i čista.

2833
01:14:43,780 --> 01:14:46,240
 Operacija oluja,

2834
01:14:46,240 --> 01:14:47,700
 Srbi moji dragi.

2835
01:14:47,700 --> 01:14:48,880
 Evo, dragi moji Srbi,

2836
01:14:48,880 --> 01:14:49,600
 sad ću vam reći.

2837
01:14:50,580 --> 01:14:52,940
 E, pa zato je ovdje svijednik

2838
01:14:52,940 --> 01:14:54,040
 i to da spasimo

2839
01:14:54,040 --> 01:14:55,040
 srpske živote

2840
01:14:55,040 --> 01:14:56,100
 od srpske politike

2841
01:14:56,100 --> 01:14:56,740
 jer ste htjeli,

2842
01:14:56,740 --> 01:14:57,780
 vaša politika,

2843
01:14:57,780 --> 01:14:58,540
 da mi pobijemo

2844
01:14:58,540 --> 01:15:00,680
 40 do 50 tisuća Srba,

2845
01:15:00,680 --> 01:15:01,640
 da bi vi pokazali,

2846
01:15:01,640 --> 01:15:02,960
 to su Englezu vas rekli,

2847
01:15:02,960 --> 01:15:04,140
 da bi mi pokazali,

2848
01:15:04,140 --> 01:15:05,180
 da bi vi pokazali

2849
01:15:05,180 --> 01:15:06,880
 kako su mi genocidni narod.

2850
01:15:06,880 --> 01:15:07,880
 Eto ga.

2851
01:15:07,880 --> 01:15:10,040
 I zato se operacija oluja

2852
01:15:10,040 --> 01:15:12,000
 proučava na svim školama strategije.

2853
01:15:12,000 --> 01:15:14,560
 I to je način kako se završava rat.

2854
01:15:14,560 --> 01:15:17,220
 To je kako se treba završiti.

2855
01:15:17,220 --> 01:15:18,940
 E tako treba završiti

2856
01:15:18,940 --> 01:15:20,000
 Ukrajinu.

2857
01:15:20,000 --> 01:15:21,780
 Ako to ove godine

2858
01:15:21,780 --> 01:15:23,160
 ne napravi

2859
01:15:23,160 --> 01:15:26,720
 rusko posto,

2860
01:15:26,720 --> 01:15:28,480
 političko i vojnu,

2861
01:15:28,480 --> 01:15:29,960
 onda

2862
01:15:29,960 --> 01:15:32,720
 pitanje što će se sve dogoditi,

2863
01:15:32,720 --> 01:15:33,980
 onda će dati uvjeta,

2864
01:15:33,980 --> 01:15:36,020
 onda će oni se na zapadu

2865
01:15:36,020 --> 01:15:37,040
 krivo protumačiti,

2866
01:15:37,040 --> 01:15:38,580
 jer Rusija je troma,

2867
01:15:38,580 --> 01:15:41,180
 ali Rusija se plati veliku cijenu,

2868
01:15:41,180 --> 01:15:42,500
 onda se dođe sebi,

2869
01:15:42,500 --> 01:15:44,100
 onda se oni stvarno

2870
01:15:44,100 --> 01:15:45,640
 znaju ratovati dugo.

2871
01:15:45,640 --> 01:15:46,920
 Ako iko zna dugo ratovati,

2872
01:15:46,920 --> 01:15:47,820
 onda to znaju Rusi.

2873
01:15:47,820 --> 01:15:49,020
 To se odmah razumijemo.

2874
01:15:49,020 --> 01:15:50,300
 Jer oni su na neki način

2875
01:15:50,300 --> 01:15:51,760
 svoj spremni na žrtvu.

2876
01:15:51,760 --> 01:15:53,020
 Na neki način uvijek.

2877
01:15:53,020 --> 01:15:54,760
 E onda će oni,

2878
01:15:54,760 --> 01:15:55,560
 ako to ne bude,

